    <section class="about">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>👕 What It Does</h2>
        <p>
          The <strong>Wardrobe Suggestion App</strong> is a simple web app that helps users choose outfits based on:
          <ul>
            <li>Clothes they already have</li>
            <li>Current weather</li>
            <li>Type of event or situation</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        <p>Users can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>✅ Upload pictures of their clothes</li>
          <li>✅ Categorize them (shirts, pants, etc.)</li>
          <li>✅ Get daily outfit suggestions based on temperature and weather</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>🛠️ Technologies We Used</h2>
        <p>
          We built this project using:
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Node + Express </strong>(Backend) </li>
            <li><strong>MongoDB </strong>(Database to store clothes) </li>
            <li><strong>Cloudinary </strong>(To store & manage images of clothes) </li>
            <li><strong>EJS </strong>(To display user-friendly pages) </li>
          </ul>
        </p>

